				p This Privacy Policy was last modified on September 29th, 2016.

				p MadKudu Inc., a Delaware corporation ("MadKudu", "us", "we", or "our") operates http://www.madkudu.com (the "Site").

				p This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the Site.

